graph TD
    Start([Start: Recruiter describes role in chat])
    Extract[AI extracts structured fields from text/voice/JD]
    Validate{Required fields present?<br/>title, skills, headcount}
    AskMore[Ask follow-up question in chat]
    BuildVO[Build value objects:<br/>RoleSpec, ExperienceRange, Headcount]
    InvariantCheck{Pass aggregate invariants?<br/>headcount>0, expMin<=expMax}
    Reject[Return 422 with validation errors]
    Construct[NewHiringIntent: status=Drafted]
    Persist[Repository.Save in transaction]
    Event[Publish IntentDrafted event via outbox]
    Resp[Return 201 Created with IntentDTO]
    End([End: Drafted intent ready for review])

    Start --> Extract
    Extract --> Validate
    Validate -->|No| AskMore
    AskMore --> Start
    Validate -->|Yes| BuildVO
    BuildVO --> InvariantCheck
    InvariantCheck -->|No| Reject
    InvariantCheck -->|Yes| Construct
    Construct --> Persist
    Persist --> Event
    Event --> Resp
    Resp --> End
